data.meta_description:
2,006 likes, 9 comments - alan__rickman__ on February 26, 2024: "What’s the best line you’ve ever uttered in a film?

Alan Rickman: “Well, in a TV series years ago, it was my character’s exit line from the whole thing and he turned to these two people who’d just trounced him and said, ‘May you both live forever!’”
(The interview for Handbag.com, 2003)

“The Barchester Chronicles”, 1982

#alanrickman #ar__interview #ar__1982 #ar__2003 #ar__barchesterchronicles".
